<header class="header">
	<h1> polished</h1>
	<h2 class="subtitle">A lightweight toolset for writing styles in JavaScript</h2>
	<a class="button" href="https://github.com/styled-components/polished"><img src="/assets/GitHub-Mark-Light-64px.png" />View on GitHub</a>
	<a class="button" href="/docs/">Docs</a>
</header>

<main class="main">
	<h3>Try editing the code below</h3>
	<pre class="repl hljs javascript">
		<code class="repl__section"><%= highlight(`
const styles = {
  color: lighten('#000', 20),
  fontSize: modularScale(1),
  [hiDPI(1.5)]: {
    fontSize: modularScale(1.25)
  }
}`) %></code>
		<code class="repl__section"><%= highlight(`
const styles = {
  color: '#333',
  fontSize: '16px',
  '@media only screen and': {
    fontSize: '20px'
  }
}`) %></code>
	</pre>
</main>

<footer>
	<p>Made by [@mxstbr](https://github.com/mxstbr), [@bhough](https://github.com/bhough), [@nikgraf](https://github.com/nikgraf) and [collaborators](https://github.com/styled-components/polished).
</footer>
